              "body": "There is [instBooleanRingAsBoolRing](https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/BooleanRing.html#instBooleanRingAsBoolRing) if you do want the Boolean ring structure with +, *. I do want the Boolean algebra structure with sup and inf here to build the OrderIsos with Clopens in PrimeSpectrum in #20533. (Interesting to note that the formula for sup is a+b-ab but for + it is a+b-2ab, because + is xor.",
